                <div class="space-y-3 lg:space-y-4 scroll-animate scroll-animate-delay-1">
                    <details class="group bg-white rounded-xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm overflow-hidden" open>
                        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-5 font-bold text-sm text-slate-900 cursor-pointer list-none hover:bg-slate-50 transition">
                            Mengapa Algoritma XGBoost?
                            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180 text-slate-400">
                                <svg fill="none" height="20" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20">
                                    <path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path>
                                </svg>
                            </span>
                        </summary>
                        <div class="px-5 pb-5 border-t border-slate-100 pt-4 text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                            XGBoost (Extreme Gradient Boosting) adalah algoritma tree-boosting yang andal untuk dataset medis tabular. Ia mengelola korelasi antar variabel klinis, menangani outlier secara efektif, dan menghasilkan hasil yang sangat dapat diinterpretasi melalui feature importance.
                        </div>
                    </details>

                    <details class="group bg-white rounded-xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm overflow-hidden">
                        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-5 font-bold text-sm text-slate-900 cursor-pointer list-none hover:bg-slate-50 transition">
                            Apa saja 22 parameter yang dievaluasi?
                            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180 text-slate-400">
                                <svg fill="none" height="20" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20">
                                    <path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path>
                                </svg>
                            </span>
                        </summary>
                        <div class="px-5 pb-5 border-t border-slate-100 pt-4 text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                            Model mengevaluasi: Usia, Gender, BMI, Aktivitas Fisik, Kualitas Tidur, Kualitas Diet, Merokok, Alkohol, Diabetes, Hipertensi, Penyakit Kardiovaskular, Depresi, Cedera Kepala, Riwayat Keluarga Alzheimer, Skor MMSE, Skor ADL, Penilaian Fungsional, Keluhan Memori, Masalah Perilaku, Tekanan Sistolik, Tekanan Diastolik, dan Kolesterol Total.
                        </div>
                    </details>

                    <details class="group bg-white rounded-xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm overflow-hidden">
                        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-5 font-bold text-sm text-slate-900 cursor-pointer list-none hover:bg-slate-50 transition">
                            Bagaimana skor risiko dihitung?
                            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180 text-slate-400">
                                <svg fill="none" height="20" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20">
                                    <path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path>
                                </svg>
                            </span>
                        </summary>
                        <div class="px-5 pb-5 border-t border-slate-100 pt-4 text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                            Skor risiko dihitung menggunakan matriks probabilitas berbobot berdasarkan temuan feature importance. Parameter seperti skor MMSE rendah, ADL buruk, riwayat keluarga genetik, dan kebiasaan gaya hidup tidak sehat mengakumulasi skor risiko lebih tinggi.
                        </div>
                    </details>

                    <details class="group bg-white rounded-xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm overflow-hidden">
                        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-5 font-bold text-sm text-slate-900 cursor-pointer list-none hover:bg-slate-50 transition">
                            Apakah data pasien aman?
                            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180 text-slate-400">
                                <svg fill="none" height="20" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20">
                                    <path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path>
                                </svg>
                            </span>
                        </summary>
                        <div class="px-5 pb-5 border-t border-slate-100 pt-4 text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                            Data pasien diproses secara lokal pada server Anda dan disimpan di database MySQL lokal. Tidak ada data yang dikirim ke server eksternal. Sistem ini dirancang untuk penggunaan internal di fasilitas kesehatan.
                        </div>
                    </details>
                </div>
